I'm the druid in that group, and that would be some good exps! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uviliu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Viliu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/02 8:14:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1338.topic&index=48>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Necros and Twitching</span><hr size=1> I can not begin to say how angry I am with Mags. Many necromancers have enough trouble getting into pickup groups and on raids in large part because of ignorance and here he is adding to it. I'm going to leave off the child molesting comments they are just too insane to even being to address. <br>
